Name: Convert NM
Description: Converts Fortran power, IF constructs, and inserts semicolons into mrgsolve model DSL code, then adds spaces around the assignment operator. Requires a selection.
Binding: addin_preprocess
Interactive: false

Name: Convert pow
Description: Converts ** to pow() in mrgsolve model DSL code in the active editor. Requires a selection.
Binding: addin_convert_pow
Interactive: false

Name: Add semicolons
Description: Inserts semicolons into mrgsolve model DSL code in the active editor. Requires a selection.
Binding: addin_add_semicolons
Interactive: false
